= Deleting items from Array State

Objective: When the user clicks "Delete" next to the todo, it should disappear from the todo list.

App.js

1 ) Delete the selected todo (with id equal todoId) from the existing todos array 

— Use the setTodos function with the previous state as the first argument and return a new todos array where todos with id equal to todoId are deleted
— To delete todo with particular id you can use filter method